column6: Now You Know (NYK) is a civic media platform which aims to provide relevant information for the Filipino people.
column31: MANILA, Philippines — Nueva Ecija Rep. Estrellita Suansing called out the Food and Drug Administration (FDA) on Wednesday for what she called the “premature” issuance of regulations governing vapor products and heated tobacco products (HTPs) as public consultations on the matter had not even been completed. According to Suansing, the FDA issued Administrative Order No. 2020-0055, which was signed on Dec. 1, 2020, but was only posted on its website last Jan. 4. I via Inquirer.nwt #NowYouKnow #NYK
